reviewText: Brought back so many memories. But tape didn't even play till the end and sounded warped.

this video is perfect! it is hilarious and creative. my kids loved it. it is educational and even gets them exercising. very thought provoking for the toddler/ little kid. you'd be lucky to get this for your child...A++++++++++++++++++++
This was one of my favorite childhood video.  I was so thrilled when I found it on Amazon!  I can't wait for my daughter to watch it and I hope she enjoys it as much as I did.
